oods Resort Casino 301|NHA]]<br><small>24</small>\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Gander Outdoors 400|POC]]<br><small>33</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Go Bowling at The Glen|GLN]]<br><small>25</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Consumers Energy 400|MCH]]<br><small>23</small>\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Bass Pro Shops NRA Night Race|BRI]]<br><small>38</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Bojangles' Southern 500|DAR]]<br><small>26</small>\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Brickyard 400|IND]]<br><small>38</small>\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[2018 South Point 400|LVS]]<br><small>38</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Federated Auto Parts 400|RCH]]<br><small>27</small>\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Bank of America Roval 400|CLT]]<br><small>36</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Gander Outdoors 400 (Dover)|DOV]]<br><small>23</small>\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[2018 1000Bulbs.com 500|TAL]]<br><small>19</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Hollywood Casino 400|KAN]]<br><small>26</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 First Data 500|MAR]]<br><small>34</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 AAA Texas 500|TEX]]<br><small>25</small>\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[2018 Can-Am 500|PHO]]<br><small>10</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2018 Ford EcoBoost 400|HOM]]<br><small>21</small>\n! 28th\n! 471\n! <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racing-reference.info/drivdet/wallada01/2018/W|title=Darrell Wallace Jr. \u2013 2018 Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=October 30, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! [[2019 Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series|2019]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[2019 Daytona 500|DAY]]<br><small>38</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2019 Folds of Honor QuikTrip 500|ATL]]<br><small>27</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[2019 Pennzoil 400|LVS]]<br><small>26</s