maryStyle|Tampa Bay Buccaneers 97thru13|border=2}};text-align:center;\n |state=autocollapse\n |title=Week Eight: Carolina Panthers at Tampa Bay Buccaneers&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n |date=October 24\n |time=8:25 p.m. EDT\n |road='''Panthers'''\n |R1=7|R2=7|R3=7|R4=10\n |home=Buccaneers\n |H1=3|H2=3|H3=0|H4=7\n |stadium=Raymond James Stadium, Tampa, Florida\n |attendance=59,073\n |weather=Cloudy, {{convert|70|F|C}}\n |referee=[[Jerome Boger]]\n |TV=[[Thursday Night Football|NFLN]]\n |TVAnnouncers=[[Brad Nessler]], [[Mike Mayock]] and [[Alex Flanagan]]\n |reference=[http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2013102400/2013/REG8/panthers@buccaneers Recap], [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/55944/TB_Gamebook.pdf Game book]\n |scoring=\n'''First quarter'''\n*CAR \u2013 [[Greg Olsen (American football)|Greg Olsen]] 1-yard pass from [[Cam Newton]] ([[Graham Gano]] kick), 4:44. ''Panthers 7\u20130. '''Drive: 15 plays, 70 yards, 8:52.'''''\n*TB \u2013 [[Rian Lindell]] 47-yard field goal, 1:24. ''Panthers 7\u20133. '''Drive: 8 plays, 51 yards, 3:20.'''''\n'''Second quarter'''\n*CAR \u2013 [[DeAngelo Williams]] 12-yard run (Graham Gano kick), 12:42. ''Panthers 14\u20133. '''Drive: 6 plays, 80 yards, 3:42.'''''\n*TB \u2013 Rian Lindell 48-yard field goal, 4:03. ''Panthers 14\u20136. '''Drive: 10 plays, 43 yards, 4:49.'''''\n'''Third quarter'''\n*CAR \u2013 Cam Newton 6-yard run (Graham Gano kick), 6:27. ''Panthers 21\u20136. '''Drive: 9 plays, 53 yards, 4:36.'''''\n'''Fourth quarter'''\n*CAR \u2013 [[Mike Tolbert]] 3-yard pass from Cam Newton (Graham Gano kick), 14:55. ''Panthers 28\u20136. '''Drive: 4 plays, 29 yards, 2:01.'''''\n*CAR \u2013 Graham Gano 29-yard field goal, 6:14. ''Panthers 31\u20136. '''Drive: 4 plays, 5 yards, 1:37.'''''\n*TB \u2013 [[Tim Wright (American football)|Tim Wright]] 10-yard pass from [[Mike Glennon]] (Rian Lindell kick), 2:53. ''Panthers 31\u201313. '''Drive: 11 plays, 81 yards, 3:21.'''''\n |stats=\n'''Top passers'''\n*CAR \u2013 [[Cam Newton]] \u2013 23/32, 221 yards, 2 TD\n*TB \u2013 [[Mike Glennon]] \u2013 30/51, 275 yards, TD\n'''Top rushers'''\n*CAR \u2013 [[Cam Newton]] \u2013 11 rushes, 50 yards, TD\n*TB \u2013 [[Mike James (American football)|Mike James]] \u2013 10 rushes, 39 yards\n'''Top receivers'''\n*CAR \u2013 [[Ted Ginn Jr.]] \u2013 5 receptions, 80 yards\n*TB \u2013 [[Vincent Jackson]] \u2013 5 receptions, 79 yards\n}}\n[[Cam Newton]] threw for 221 yards and two touchdown passes, and rushed for another touchdown, as Carolina defeated Tampa Bay 31\u201313. The Buccaneers failed to enter the [[Red zone (gridiron football)|red zone]] until the final three minutes of the game. [[Doug Martin (running back)|Doug Martin]] sat out the game with an injured shoulder. \n\nWith the loss, Tampa Bay fell to 0\u20137.\n\n====Week 9: at Seattle Seahawks====\n\n{{Americanfootballbox\n |titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Tampa Bay Buccaneers 97thru13|border=2}};text-align:center;\n |state=autocollapse\n |title=Week Nine: Tampa Bay Buccaneers at Seattle Seahawks&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n |date=November 3\n |time=4:05 p.m. EST/1:05 p.m. [[Pacific Time Zone|PST]]\n |road=Buccaneers\n |R1=0|R2=21|R3=3|R4=0|R5=0\n |home='''Seahawks'''\n |H1=0|H2=7|H3=7|H4=10|H5=3\n |stadium=[[CenturyLink Field]], [[Seattle, Washington]]\n |attendance=67,873\n |weather=Sunny, {{convert|48|F|C}}\n |referee=[[Mike Carey (American football)|Mike Carey]]\n |TV=Fox\n |TVAnnouncers=[[Kenny Albert]], [[Daryl Johnston]] and [[Tony Siragusa]]\n |reference=[http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2013110307/2013/REG9/buccaneers@seahawks Recap], [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/55965/SEA_Gamebook.pdf Game book]\n |scoring=\n'''First quarter'''\n* ''No scoring plays.''\n'''Second quarter'''\n*TB \u2013 [[Tim Wright (American football)|Tim Wright]] 12-yard pass from [[Mike Glennon]] ([[Rian Lindell]] kick), 11:50. ''Buccaneers 7\u20130. '''Drive: 10 plays, 90 yards, 6:03.'''''\n*TB \u2013 [[Tiquan Underwood]] 20-yard pass from Mike Glennon (Rian Lindell k